  m_Name: Day 3 Daughter Messages
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  personSpokenTo: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 08a894b9b170bd4408c3738b6b563b07, type: 2}
  delayBetweenMessages: 1
  lines:
  - "Hi Dad! Hope works been good to you today, sorry I\u2019ve been very busy again,
    so I can\u2019t reply."
  - "I got to teach a bunch of the kids about things they\u2019d learn in school,
    afterlife (lack of it!) and how much you should treasure your life, spending
    it creating a family that can spread the same joy of to their children. "
  - "It\u2019s been good preparation for the future for the both of us, and has helped
    calm them down a lot."
  - "Just like yesterday, good luck and stay safe! I\u2019ve seen a lot more people
    evacuated, because of your no efforts no doubt."
